      "text": "👁️ Perceive: User asks about weather\n🧠 Decide: I need to call the weather API tool\n⚡ Act: Call weather_tool(location=\"Sydney\")\n👁️ Perceive: Tool returns \"25°C, sunny\"\n🧠 Decide: I have the answer, respond to user\n⚡ Act: \"It's 25°C and sunny in Sydney!\"",
